summary:
This is a mod for MMOxReview, inspired by Terror Soldier\'s Exploding Braith mod!
Totally not lore friendly.
Just for fun.
descriptionHtml:
Because of all the exploding Braiths in Skyrim, Ultra Braith has spawned!
She has replaced Jenassa as the local hireling at the Drunken Huntsman in Whiterun.
She\'s pretty much all grown up now and pretty freaking invulnerable.
She wields the greataxe Braithbringer, and carries a copy just for you, Dovahkiin!

Enjoy!
author: ordersomething
